wf_activity.name: Submission to Verscend and Notification to Account Team

sys_variable_value.value: // Set 'answer' to the number of seconds this timer should wait answer = 0;

1. Report/document needs to be created with applicable information for Verscend. 2. Download from Service Now to temporary location on desktop: Report/document, group structure, enrollment, carrier reports. 3. Open VT Connect Ticket uploading: Report/document, group structure, enrollment, carrier reports. 4. Forward VT Connect email notification to Verscend Team, copy 3DSupport Team. 5. Update VT Connect Case# field in Request 6. Communication to account team that data request is in motion and estimated timeframe when data will be in staging 7. Move to Waiting for Data Feed stage. 8. Update Current Status field in Group Table to: New Group - Waiting for Data Feed
